<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٥٦٣ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4511">عَلِيُّ بْنُ الْجَعْدِ </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2511">أَبِي حَازِمٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ <span class="c2">«مَا عَابَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> طَعَامًا قَطُّ إِنِ اشْتَهَاهُ أَكَلَهُ وَإِلَّا تَرَكَهُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>